  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aimed to investigate the preemptive analgesia efficacy of of preemptive pregabalin
      for the postoperative pain management after radiofrequency ablation (RFA) of liver cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Our data will investigate if preemptive administration of pregabalin will have a role in
      reducing postoperative pain after radiofrequency ablation (RFA) of liver cancer.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
